<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢٧٠٤ - حد الطريق <span class="c2">(٣)</span> سبعة أذرع.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(صحيح)</span> <span class="c2">(طس)</span> عن جابر. <span class="c2">(الصحيحة ٣٩٦٠)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
